c: 6
v: 93
t: Qui est malus than 1 qui fabricates lies attributes them DEUS dictus ego received divine inspiration when non such inspiration dedit eum dictus ego scripsit same prout deus revelations? unus vos vide transgressors decessus! angels extend their manus to them dictus Let iit de tuus anima! Hodie vos incurred shameful retribution pro dictus DEUS truth ac est too arrogant accept His revelations